  m_text: "Highlights the room's Key Wall. \n\nA Key Wall has two requirements: It's
    the longest wall in the room, and more importantly, has NO other room points
    behind it.\n\nWith a Key Wall, an artist can craft a more \"stage-like\" environment,
    avoiding the obligation of procedural art"
